{
  "id": "RAW_c4f23f",
  "title": "智谱发布 GLM-4.5V，全球开源多模态推理新标杆，Day0 推理微调实战教程到！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTM5NTg2OA==&mid=2247505554&idx=1&sn=7f44328b06a8d3ed7aa8d872838942a3",
  "date": "2025-08-11 14:27:00",
  "author": "魔搭ModelScope社区",
  "siteName": "魔搭ModelScope社区",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span>\n   <br></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1b9886b2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8ZLuyaibrZblZcXFuBpOyibndcB65RibPE6huaZUW09kY3VcMT38KDehiabjYFKrgwFuCBkyjICfjibgRvOAYdmpWqQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"jP2lRYjQb932AO8g\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">视觉语言大模型（VLM）已经成为智能系统的关键基石。随着真实世界的智能任务越来越复杂，VLM模型也亟需在基本的多模态感知之外，逐渐增强复杂任务中的推理能力，提升自身的准确性、全面性和智能化程度，使得复杂问题解决、长上下文理解、多模态智能体等智能任务成为可能。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <h2 style=\"text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">刚刚，智谱发布了最新的&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">GLM-4.5V</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">开源工作——</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">全球100B级效果最佳的开源视觉推理模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，已同步在魔搭社区开源。</span></span></span></h2>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型合集：</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://modelscope.cn/collections/GLM-45V-8b471c8f97154e\" target=\"_blank\">https://modelscope.cn/collections/GLM-45V-8b471c8f97154e</a></span></span></span><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">GLM-4.5V 基于智谱新一代旗舰文本基座模型 GLM-4.5-Air（106B参数，12B激活），延续 GLM-4.1V-Thinking 技术路线，在 42 个公开视觉多模态榜单中综合效果达到同级别开源模型 SOTA 性能，涵盖图像、视频、文档理解以及 GUI Agent 等常见任务。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\"></span><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100021899\" data-ratio=\"0.9796296296296296\" style=\"width:747px;height:731.8265625px;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0e144029&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8ZLuyaibrZblZcXFuBpOyibndcB65RibPE6DtNaickWQtfIAHGz5XghYl4qFMOb90ONXjLbTg0CGMfpCpPzEZINtzg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span data-type=\"text\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在多模态榜单之外，研究团队更重视模型在真实场景下的表现与可用性。GLM-4.5V 通过高效混合训练，具备覆盖不同种视觉内容的处理能力，实现全场景视觉推理，包括：</span></span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type:disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">图像推理（场景理解、复杂多图分析、位置识别）</span></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">视频理解（长视频分镜分析、事件识别）</span></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">GUI 任务（屏幕读取、图标识别、桌面操作辅助）</span></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">复杂图表与长文档解析（研报分析、信息提取）</span></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Grounding 能力（精准定位视觉元素）</span></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同时，模型新增 “思考模式” 开关，用户可灵活选择快速响应或深度推理，平衡效率与效果，该开关的使用方式与GLM-4.5 语言模型相同。</span></span></span></p>\n   <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:10px auto;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:flex;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;justify-content:center;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 3px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);visibility: visible;transform: skew(-10deg);\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 5px 18px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;display: flex;align-items: center;visibility: visible;transform: skew(10deg);\">\n       <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">模型推理</span></span></strong></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"> \n         <br> \n        </span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <h1 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\"></p>\n   </h1>\n   <h1 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n    <pre><code data-syntax=\"plaintext\" data-theme=\"default\"><p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">环境安装</span></span></strong></p></code></pre>\n    <p></p>\n   </h1>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对于</span></span></span><code data-type=\"inlineCode\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">SGLang</span></span></span></code><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">和</span></span></span><code data-type=\"inlineCode\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">transformers</span></span></span></code><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span></span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\">git&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">clone</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-V.git\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-V.git</a></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">cd</span>&nbsp;GLM-</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">pip install -r requirements.txt</span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <pre><code data-syntax=\"plaintext\" data-theme=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">vLLM</span></span></code></pre>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"apache\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">pip</span>&nbsp;install -U vllm --pre --extra-index-url <a href=\"https://wheels.vllm.ai/nightly\" target=\"_blank\">https://wheels.vllm.ai/nightly</a></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">pip</span>&nbsp;install transformers-v4.<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">55</span>.<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>-GLM-<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">4</span>.<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">5</span>V-preview</span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <pre><code data-syntax=\"plaintext\" data-theme=\"default\" style=\"height:undefinedpx;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code></pre>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size:14pt;line-height:1.45;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">vLLM推理</span></span></span></h3>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"sql\"><code><span leaf=\"\">vllm serve zai<span class=\"code-snippet__operator\">-</span>org<span class=\"code-snippet__operator\">/</span>GLM<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">-4.5</span>V \\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--tensor-parallel-size 4 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--tool-call-parser glm45 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--reasoning-parser glm45 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--enable-auto-tool-choice \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--served-model-name glm-4.5v \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--allowed-local-media-path / \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--media-io-kwargs '{\"video\": {\"num_frames\": -1}}'</span></span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <pre><code data-syntax=\"plaintext\" data-theme=\"default\" style=\"height:undefinedpx;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code></pre>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size:14pt;line-height:1.45;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">SGlang推理</span></span></span></h3>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"css\"><code><span leaf=\"\">python3 -m sglang<span class=\"code-snippet__selector-class\">.launch_server</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">--model-path</span>&nbsp;zai-org/GLM-<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">4.5</span>V \\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">--tp-size</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">4</span>&nbsp;\\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">--tool-call-parser</span>&nbsp;glm45 \\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">--reasoning-parser</span>&nbsp;glm45 \\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">--served-model-name</span>&nbsp;glm-<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">4.5</span>v \\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">--port</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">8000</span>&nbsp;\\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">--host</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0.0</span>.<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0.0</span></span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <pre><code data-syntax=\"plaintext\" data-theme=\"default\" style=\"height:undefinedpx;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code><br><div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:10px auto;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:flex;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;justify-content:center;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 3px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);visibility: visible;transform: skew(-10deg);\"><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 5px 18px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;display: flex;align-items: center;visibility: visible;transform: skew(10deg);\"><p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">模型微调</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p></div></div></div></div><h1 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><p data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\"></p></h1><h1 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><p data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p><pre><code data-syntax=\"plaintext\" data-theme=\"default\"><p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们介绍使用ms-swift对GLM-4.5V进行训练。ms-swift是魔搭社区官方提供的大模型与多模态大模型训练部署框架。</span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ms-swift开源地址：</span></span></strong></p></code><br></pre><p></p></h1><p></p><p><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/modelscope/ms-swift\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/modelscope/ms-swift</a></span></span></span><span data-type=\"text\"></span></p></pre>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究团队将展示可运行的微调demo，并给出自定义数据集的格式。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在开始微调之前，请确保您的环境已准备妥当。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># pip install git+<a href=\"https://github.com/modelscope/ms-swift.git\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/modelscope/ms-swift.git</a></span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">git&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">clone</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/modelscope/ms-swift.git\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/modelscope/ms-swift.git</a></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">cd</span>&nbsp;ms-swift</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">pip install -e .</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">pip install git+<a href=\"https://github.com/huggingface/transformers.git\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/huggingface/transformers.git</a></span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <pre><code data-syntax=\"shell\" data-theme=\"default\" style=\"height:undefinedpx;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code></pre>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"background-color:initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如果您需要自定义数据集微调模型，你可以将数据准备成以下格式。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"json\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">\"messages\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">[{</span><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">\"role\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"user\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">,</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">\"content\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"&lt;image&gt;&lt;image&gt;What is the difference between the two images?\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">},</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">\"role\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"assistant\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">,</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">\"content\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"The first one is a kitten, and the second one is a puppy.\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">}],</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">\"images\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"/xxx/x.jpg\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">,</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"/xxx/x.png\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">]}</span></span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <pre><code data-syntax=\"shell\" data-theme=\"default\" style=\"height:undefinedpx;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code></pre>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">训练脚本：</span></span></span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"sql\"><code><span leaf=\"\">#&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">4</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__operator\">*</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">65</span>GiB</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES<span class=\"code-snippet__operator\">=</span><span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>,<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">1</span>,<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">2</span>,<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">3</span>&nbsp;\\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">swift sft \\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--model ZhipuAI/GLM-4.5V \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--dataset 'AI-ModelScope/LaTeX_OCR:human_handwrite#20000' \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--split_dataset_ratio 0.01 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--train_type lora \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--torch_dtype bfloat16 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--num_train_epochs 1 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--per_device_train_batch_size 1 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--per_device_eval_batch_size 1 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--learning_rate 1e-4 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--lora_rank 8 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--lora_alpha 32 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--target_modules all-linear \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--freeze_vit true \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--gradient_accumulation_steps 16 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--eval_steps 50 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--save_steps 50 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--save_total_limit 2 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--logging_steps 5 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--max_length 2048 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--output_dir output \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--warmup_ratio 0.05 \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--dataloader_num_workers 4</span></span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <pre><code data-syntax=\"shell\" data-theme=\"default\" style=\"height:undefinedpx;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code></pre>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\"></span><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100021898\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2111111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:748px;height:158.2537764350453px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eca36daa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8ZLuyaibrZblZcXFuBpOyibndcB65RibPE6M0EEaU0wSwicO1Z04XHYU6kibcoUoViaqECyBOj78jxLaLyDyOzO0hafg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span data-type=\"text\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">训练完成后，使用以下命令</span></span></span><span data-type=\"text\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">进行推理：</span></span></span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"sql\"><code><span leaf=\"\">CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES<span class=\"code-snippet__operator\">=</span><span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>&nbsp;\\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">swift infer \\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--adapters output/vx-xxx/checkpoint-xxx \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--stream true \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--load_data_args true \\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">--max_new_tokens 2048</span></span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <pre><code data-syntax=\"shell\" data-theme=\"default\" style=\"height:undefinedpx;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code></pre>\n   <p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;margin-left:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">推送模型到ModelScope：</span></span></span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\">swift&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">export</span>&nbsp;\\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; --adapters output/vx-xxx/checkpoint-xxx \\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; --push_to_hub&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__literal\">true</span>&nbsp;\\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; --hub_model_id&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">'&lt;your-model-id&gt;'</span>&nbsp;\\</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; --hub_token&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">'&lt;your-sdk-token&gt;'</span></span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <pre><code data-syntax=\"shell\" data-theme=\"default\" style=\"height:undefinedpx;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code></pre>\n   <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">点击</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">阅读原文，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;即可跳转模型合集~</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱发布了 GLM-4.5V，一款基于 GLM-4.5-Air 的全球 100B 级开源视觉推理模型，并在多个视觉多模态榜单中达到 SOTA，同时提供了详细的推理和微调实战教程。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱发布了 GLM-4.5V，一款基于 GLM-4.5-Air 的全球 100B 级开源视觉推理模型，并在多个视觉多模态榜单中达到 SOTA，同时提供了详细的推理和微调实战教程。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了智谱最新发布的 GLM-4.5V 开源多模态模型，该模型基于智谱新一代文本基座模型 GLM-4.5-Air（106B 参数，12B 激活），并在 42 个公开视觉多模态榜单中综合效果达到同级别开源模型 SOTA 性能。GLM-4.5V 通过高效混合训练，具备全场景视觉推理能力，涵盖图像推理、视频理解、GUI 任务、复杂图表与长文档解析以及 Grounding 能力。文章强调了模型在真实场景下的表现与可用性，并新增了“思考模式”开关，允许用户灵活平衡效率与效果。此外，文章提供了详细的 Day0 推理实战教程（支持 vLLM 和 SGLang），以及基于 ms-swift 框架的模型微调指南，包括环境搭建、自定义数据集格式和训练脚本示例，极大降低了开发者的使用门槛，方便用户快速上手进行模型部署和定制化训练。",
